        },
        {
            "title": "在斯塔默與習近平會晤後 川普警告英國與中國做生意「很危險」",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國總統唐納德·川普警告英國和加拿大不要與中國達成新的商業協議。這兩國領導人本月先後訪問北京，試圖深化與世界第二大經濟體中國的關係。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普周四晚間在回答記者關於英國首相基爾·斯塔默本周訪問中國的問題時說道：「他們這樣做很危險。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「加拿大與中國做生意就更危險了。」川普補充說，「加拿大表現不好。他們表現非常糟糕，你不能指望中國能解決他們的問題。」他當時在華盛頓出席一部關於第一夫人梅拉尼婭·川普的紀錄片首映式。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-140d2330-412b-362f-aee5-328020f6e859-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在川普的批評之前幾個小時，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:斯塔默;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/斯塔默\">斯塔默</a>與中國領導人習近平會晤，並在英國企業擴大中國市場准入方面取得了進展。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周五在北京，斯塔默告訴商界領袖，他與習近平舉行了「非常熱情」的會晤，達到了預期的「溝通水平」。斯塔默稱讚免簽旅行協議和降低威士忌關稅是「非常重要的行動，象征著我們正在努力改善兩國關係」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">斯塔默的訪問緊隨加拿大領導人馬克·卡尼之後。卡尼取消了之前為與美國關稅保持一致而對中國電動汽車徵收的關稅。此舉引發了川普的強烈反對，並威脅如果加拿大成為中國產品的「後門」，則對加拿大商品徵收100%的關稅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：恢復高級別安全對話、增設人民幣清算行 中國發布斯塔默訪華11項成果</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump Warns UK on ‘Dangerous’ China Moves After Xi-Starmer Talks</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Natalie Choy.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9C%A8%E6%96%AF%E5%A1%94%E9%BB%98%E8%88%87%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E6%9C%83%E6%99%A4%E5%BE%8C-%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E8%88%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%81%9A%E7%94%9F%E6%84%8F-%E5%BE%88%E5%8D%B1%E9%9A%AA-022609220.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-30 10:58:04",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "蘋果公司在中國市場東山再起 創四年來最高季度銷售額",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 蘋果公司假日季在中國市場強勁反彈。得益於新機型iPhone 17的暢銷，該公司自2021年底以來首次在該地區實現了250億美元級的季度銷售額。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在截至12月27日的三個月中，該公司大中華區營收飆升38%，達到255億美元，遠超華爾街平均預期的218億美元，也遠遠超過了整體銷售額的增速。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這些數字呈現出蘋果公司的意外復甦景象。此前，該公司一直難以重振中國業務這個舊日的強勁引擎。蘋果當季實現了大中華區史上第二高營收，接近四年前創下的假日季紀錄258億美元。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7a67cffa-a0aa-3927-b026-070e5df7faa0-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">執行長蒂姆·庫克將這一表現歸功於智慧手機升級換代用戶激增。他還表示，從其他平台轉到蘋果手機的用戶數量也實現了兩位數百分比的成長。這使得大中華和大陸的在用設備量創下歷史新高。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「這是iPhone大中華區史上最佳季度，」他說，並稱iPhone 17是主力軍。該公司最新產品陣容包括iPhone 17 Pro和Pro Max，以及更纖薄的iPhone Air。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/fBBqwwR7HEQuJTjHHnZZXA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/515a853a28b3cb7fcbf3f52e59df476b\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">庫克補充說，中國零售店的客流量也實現了兩位數的成長。此外，在中國購買Apple Watch、iPad和Mac之類產品的消費者，大多是這些非iPhone產品的新用戶。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Apple Rebounds in China With Biggest Sales Quarter in Four Years</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E6%9D%B1%E5%B1%B1%E5%86%8D%E8%B5%B7-%E5%89%B5%E5%9B%9B%E5%B9%B4%E4%BE%86%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E5%AD%A3%E5%BA%A6%E9%8A%B7%E5%94%AE%E9%A1%8D-014541363.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-30 10:32:49",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "印尼證交所CEO在印尼股市大跌後辭職",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 印尼證券交易所執行長Iman Rachman宣布他將辭職。在指數編制機構MSCI Inc.發出可能對印尼股市降級的警告後，印尼股市連續兩日大跌。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Rachman辭職正值投資者對監管措施能否滿足MSCI要求仍感到不安之際。基準雅加達綜合指數周五反彈，漲幅一度達到2.2%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Indonesia Stock Exchange CEO Resigns After Market Rout</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
